quran[15]{c,v,t,f}:
  26,199,"tí ó sì ké e fún wọn, wọn kò níí gbà á gbọ́ ní òdodo."
  26,200,"Báyẹn ni A ṣe mú (àtakò) wọ inú ọkàn àwọn ẹlẹ́ṣẹ̀."
  26,201,"Wọn kò níí gbà á gbọ́ ní òdodo títí wọn yóò fi rí ìyà ẹlẹ́ta-eléro."
  33,52,"Kò lẹ́tọ̀ọ́ fún ọ (láti fẹ́) àwọn obìnrin (mìíràn) lẹ́yìn (ìsọ̀rí àwọn obìnrin tí A ti sọ ṣíwájú kò sì lẹ́tọ̀ọ́ fún ọ) láti fi àwọn obìnrin (mìíràn) pààrọ̀ wọn, kódà kí dáadáa wọn jọ ọ́ lójú, àfi àwọn ẹrú rẹ. Allāhu sì ń jẹ́ Olùṣọ́ lórí gbogbo n̄ǹkan.2 {1}",1:[Ìyẹn nínú āyah  50.]
  33,53,"Ẹ̀yin tí ẹ gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo, ẹ má ṣe wọ àwọn inú ilé Ànábì àfi tí wọ́n bá yọ̀ǹda fún yín láti wọlé jẹun láì níí jẹ́ ẹni tí yóò máa retí kí oúnjẹ jinná, ṣùgbọ́n tí wọ́n bá pè yín (fún oúnjẹ) ẹ wọ inú ilé nígbà náà. Nígbà tí ẹ bá sì jẹun tán, ẹ túká, ẹ má ṣe jókòó kalẹ̀ tira yin fún ọ̀rọ̀ kan mọ́ (nínú ilé rẹ̀). Dájúdájú ìyẹn ń kó ìnira bá Ànábì - kí ìkẹ́ àti ọlà Allāhu máa bá a -. Ó sì ń tijú yín. Allāhu kò sì níí tijú níbi òdodo. Nígbà tí ẹ bá sì fẹ́ bèèrè n̄ǹkan ní ọ̀dọ̀ àwọn ìyàwó rẹ̀, ẹ bèèrè rẹ̀ ní ọ̀dọ̀ wọn ní ẹ̀yìn gàgá. Ìyẹn jẹ́ àfọ̀mọ́ jùlọ fún ọkàn yín àti ọkàn wọn. Kò tọ́ fún yín láti kó ìnira bá Òjíṣẹ́ Allāhu. (Kò sì tọ́ fún yín) láti fẹ́ àwọn ìyàwó rẹ̀ lẹ́yìn (ikú) rẹ̀ láéláé. Dájúdájú ìyẹn jẹ́ n̄ǹkan ńlá ní ọ̀dọ̀ Allāhu."
  33,54,"Tí ẹ bá ṣàfi hàn kiní kan tàbí ẹ fi pamọ́, dájúdájú Allāhu ń jẹ́ Onímọ̀ nípa gbogbo n̄ǹkan."
  34,31,"Àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́ wí pé: “A kò níí ní ìgbàgbọ́ nínú al-Ƙur’ān yìí àti èyí tó wá ṣíwájú rẹ̀.” Tí ó bá jẹ́ pé o bá rí wọn ni nígbà tí wọ́n bá dá àwọn alábòsí dúró níwájú Olúwa wọn, (o máa rí wọn tí) apá kan wọn yóò dá ọ̀rọ̀ náà padà sí apá kan; àwọn tí wọ́n sọ di ọ̀lẹ (nínú wọn) yóò wí fún àwọn tó ṣègbéraga (nínú wọn) pé: “Tí kì í bá ṣe ẹ̀yin ni, àwa ìbá jẹ́ onígbàgbọ́ òdodo.”"
  34,32,"Àwọn tó ṣègbéraga yó sì wí fún àwọn tí wọ́n sọ di ọ̀lẹ pé: “Ṣé àwa l’a ṣẹ yín lórí kúrò nínú ìmọ̀nà lẹ́yìn tí ó dé ba yín? Rárá o! Ọ̀daràn ni yín ni.”"
  34,33,"Àwọn tí wọ́n sọ di ọ̀lẹ yó sì wí fún àwọn tó ṣègbéraga pé: “Rárá! Ète òru àti ọ̀sán (láti ọ̀dọ̀ yín ló kóbá wa) nígbà tí ẹ̀ ń pa wá ní àṣẹ pé kí á ṣàì gbàgbọ́ nínú Allāhu, kí á sì sọ (àwọn kan) di ẹgbẹ́ Rẹ̀.” Wọ́n fi àbámọ̀ wọn pamọ́ nígbà tí wọ́n rí ìyà. A sì kó ẹ̀wọ̀n sí ọrùn àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́. Ṣé A óò san wọ́n ní ẹ̀san kan bí kò ṣe ohun tí wọ́n ń ṣe níṣẹ́?"
  35,16,"Tí Ó bá fẹ́, Ó máa mu yín kúrò lórí ilẹ̀. Ó sì máa mú ẹ̀dá titun wá."
  35,17,"Ìyẹn kò sì lágbara kan lára Allāhu.1 {1}",1:[Kò kó wàhálà kan bá Allāhu Ẹlẹ́dàá.]
  35,18,"Ẹlẹ́rù ẹ̀ṣẹ̀ kan kò níí ru ẹrù ẹ̀ṣẹ̀ ẹlòmíìràn. Kódà kí ẹnì kan tí ẹrù ẹ̀ṣẹ̀ wọ̀ lọ́rùn ké sí (ẹlòmíìràn) fún àbárù ẹrù ẹ̀ṣẹ̀ rẹ̀, wọn kò níí bá a ru kiní kan nínú rẹ̀, ìbáà jẹ́ ìbátan.Àwọn tí ò ń ṣèkìlọ̀ fún ni àwọn tó ń páyà Olúwa wọn ní ìkọ̀kọ̀, tí wọ́n sì ń kírun. Ẹni tí ó bá ṣàfọ̀mọ́ (ara rẹ̀ kúrò nínú ìwà ẹ̀ṣẹ̀), ó ṣàfọ̀mọ́ fún ẹ̀mí ara rẹ̀ ni. Ọ̀dọ̀ Allāhu sì ni àbọ̀ ẹ̀dá. {1}",1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah an-Nahl;  16:25.]
  36,1,"Yā sīn (Allāhu ló mọ ohun tí Ó gbàlérò pẹ̀lú àwọn háràfí náà.)1 {1}",1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al Baƙọrah; 2:1.]
  36,2,"(Allāhu) fi Al-Ƙur’ān tí ó kún fún ọgbọ́n búra.1 {1}",1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah Yūnus; 10:1]
  36,3,"Dájúdájú ìwọ wà nínú àwọn Òjíṣẹ́."